plot: When Lex Luthor appears by Nyxly's side, Supergirl and team must deal with the emotional fallout of facing their two biggest foes at the same time. Alex makes plans for the perfect proposal to Kelly, but work keeps getting in the way.

While the Super Friends try to get the Love Totem and use the power of the other Totems to capture Nxyly, Lex reveals his motive to the imp for helping her. Andrea gives William an ultimatum, and Alex tries to make the perfect wedding proposal to Kelly.—Gislef
